Brandon Wyne, 17, and Courtney Griffith, 18, were pulled over for a broken tail light in Virginia on January 10 when they were stopped for a traffic stop .
CCTV footage captured the moment Wyne and Griffith were pulled out of the car .
The officer sprayed Wyne with pepper spray and pepper sprayed him with a Taser gun twice .
Wyne agreed to get out the car on the condition that nobody touched him until his mother arrived because he is a minor .